$interpreted: Lazer: It was right to wait until the day of the proclamation ceremony to flee. Andrew and his subordinate's vigilance has decreased.
Lazer: They must've thought you'd listen like a good little girl.
Clover: ...Godfather, if I——
Lazer: Enough. I won't let you die. I delivered you myself, you must live.
Clover: So you...you were the human slave who broke my left hand!
Clover: Why didn't you tell me..!?
Clover: The nanny who took care of me said, she didn't know why, that person not only let me live, but also left me with a sum of money...
Lazer: As I said before...mirage.
Lazer: I've arranged a meeting with the Juan family's old subordinates. You hide here for the time being.
Clover: Wait, Godfather!
Clover: ...Godfather, you always do this...
Devious: ...What is it? Still can't find Diana?
Andrew: ...We'll find her.
Devious: Hsssss. I told you not to underestimate that chameleon. You can never trust someone who betrays their own country...
Clover: But you can trust those that betray their own family?
Andrew: Diana!? I thought you already——
Clover: Fled? I decided to return. I have just one condition.
Andrew: ...Speak.
Clover: ...Take care of this country.
Andrew: ......
Devious: Ah, since the remaining contenders have arrived, let's not waste time. Let us carry out the final confirmation.
Devious: Under the witness of the Holy Snake God and Goddess, as well as that of myself and all citizens of the Desert Kingdom,
Devious: do you, Diana Juan Gomez, agree to give up your right to the throne, and to allow Andrew Juliano Gomez to become the next King?
Clover: I agree.
Devious: Excellent. Hssssss....well then, please shake hands.
Devious: The ceremony is complete, thereby marking that you, my lady, have given up your qualifications to succeed to the Gomez throne.
Clover: Clover Crystal!?
Clover: How'd it get from my...!
Andrew: Oh......
Devious: Andrew, sir!!!!!
Devious: Dead...damn!!
Devious: You rotten scum! How can you be Queen with filthy tricks like this!? I knew I shouldn't have listened to Andrew!
Clover: (No! I can't fight in front of all these people——)
Devious: You ungrateful little piece of fecal matter! He even paid for you to leave the country in ease!
Clover: Eh...?
Lazer: ——Does the High Priest want to be the first one to start a revolt?
Lazer: The rules for succeeding to the Gomez throne are that there are no rules. The last contender alive is fit to be the next ruler.
Lazer: The ceremony has not ended, and that means the competition continues——
Lazer: Before you stands Queen Diana, her Majesty. Why are you not kneeling!?
Lazer: High Priest Devious! Do you not hear me?
Lazer: This is the Queen, now kneel before her!!
